            <title>django生成图片验证码</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2018/09/2018-09-18-django%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81/</link>
